snippet.title: Abyss The Forgotten Past - Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as Leonnor who sets out on a journey to discover everything about his past and his world, things are not always what they seem! Learn special abilities, battle monsters and encounter celestial beings as you explore this beautifically crafted pixel world.

Abyss The Forgotten Past: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1369980/Abyss_The_Forgotten_Past/
